properties.Notes: 2000, page 122: "Many of the gay bars are on or near Rampart, St. Ann and Dumaine streets in the vicinity of Armstrong Park. The neighborhoods around the park are not safe, so be very careful, and don't go into the park at night unless there's a major event."
